reviews.text: Always have a pleasant experience here. The staff are helpful since it‚Äôs a to go store where you scan your order name. Food is always flavorful, fresh, and made on time. My go to is the mildy spicy shrimp pho, steamed dumplings, and egg rolls.

What I ordered : BYOP, rare beef, flank and brisket . Beef broth:  Level 2

I think the food was good, it wasn‚Äôt too spicy which I liked. The broth was well seasoned. I ordered directly on the website. The only thing I would change has nothing to do with the food. I think text updates would be good , because i thought my order was cancelled  after waiting a little while . I‚Äôd definitely order again though . You get a lot for the price, and utensils are included.

I also ordered wontons and steamed pot stickers.

Door dash review:

Was glad they opened late.  Ordered at 10:14pm.   Got here and the broth was still hot.  Decent amount of noodles and veggies.  Came with 2 packets of hoisen and Sriracha packets.

The pho was decently good.  I honestly didn't expect much from delivery pho this late at night but i was pleasantly surprised.  In a pinch I would order from here again next time.

Pictures taken inside my hotel room*

I got the tofu vegan pho on Thursday evening. Since late that night I‚Äôve had severe diarrhea, and just vomited (as of Saturday). I know with certainty it wasn‚Äôt anything else I ate. I don‚Äôt want to be mean, I understand that mistakes happen, but the only reasonable logical conclusion is that this due to some kind of cross contamination issue, given the fact you‚Äôre part of a ghost kitchen. So I felt a need to say something based on that. Please double and triple check that your equipment isn‚Äôt contaminating other food, thank you.
I‚Äôll say it tasted and looked good going down at least, but I can‚Äôt give anything higher than one star for obvious reasons :/ and the previous 2 times I had it deserved 5 stars

The broth I had in the chicken pho was not a real pho broth. Even compared to basic chicken broth, it was not good. Tasted like the scum that needs to get skimmed off the top while simmering. The taste was quite nauseating. Also did not appreciate that the sauce packets are on top of the food in the soup bowl. Its unsanitary.  I don‚Äôt want plastic sauce packets touching my food, there‚Äôs no telling where the packets are stored or where they‚Äôve been. The edamame was pretty decent though.

recentReviews.text: Always have a pleasant experience here. The staff are helpful since it‚Äôs a to go store where you scan your order name. Food is always flavorful, fresh, and made on time. My go to is the mildy spicy shrimp pho, steamed dumplings, and egg rolls.

recentReviews.author: Travis Sadler
recentReviews.text: The broth I had in the chicken pho was not a real pho broth. Even compared to basic chicken broth, it was not good. Tasted like the scum that needs to get skimmed off the top while simmering. The taste was quite nauseating. Also did not appreciate that the sauce packets are on top of the food in the soup bowl. Its unsanitary.  I don‚Äôt want plastic sauce packets touching my food, there‚Äôs no telling where the packets are stored or where they‚Äôve been. The edamame was pretty decent though.

customerMoodAnalysis.sentimentSummary: Customer opinions are divided. The 3.2/5 rating from 5 recent reviews suggests some great experiences mixed with areas needing attention.

strengthsPerceived: Customers appreciate the flavorful, fresh, and timely preparation of dishes like the mildly spicy shrimp pho, steamed dumplings, and egg rolls. - social media marketing can showcase this strength
The restaurant offers a generous portion size and includes utensils, which customers find valuable for the price. - SEO services can leverage this for better visibility
Customers are pleasantly surprised by the quality of food delivered late at night, with hot broth and a decent amount of noodles and veggies. - Boostly marketing services can amplify this
improvementOpportunities: Concerns about food safety and cross-contamination - review management can address this concern
